
-----------------------------------------

1. Check 
   $ service mysql status

2. If active run 
   $ sudo service mysql stop

3. Run
   $ sudo docker-compose up 
    
  [Here it will create the docker container and images for Zookeeper,Kafka,Springboot and Mysql]

4. After the server started run the consumer application

5. Hit the url
 
   http://localhost:9090/api/v1/start_ride

   http://localhost:9090/api/v1/pause_ride

   http://localhost:9090/api/v1/restart_ride

   http://localhost:9090/api/v1/end_ride

6. As you hit end_ride the message will be passed to the consumer service



